00:32:39,681 --> 00:32:40,646
We did it.

877
00:32:40,682 --> 00:32:47,687
<i>♪ ♪</i>

878
00:32:54,228 --> 00:32:57,496
I can't thank you enough.

879
00:32:57,532 --> 00:33:01,267
You don't have to thank me,
Leonard.

880
00:33:01,302 --> 00:33:04,503
You just have to walk out
that door.

881
00:33:04,539 --> 00:33:11,544
<i>♪ ♪</i>

882
00:33:24,125 --> 00:33:31,130
<i>♪ ♪</i>

883
00:33:36,471 --> 00:33:38,104
That was one hell
of a cross.

