00:37:08,478 --> 00:37:09,977
This is a moment
for celebration.

970
00:37:10,013 --> 00:37:11,512
That's right.

971
00:37:11,547 --> 00:37:13,659
'Cause a man's life wasn't
the only thing saved today.

